  "system": {
    "actions": [],
    "description": "<p>Effect: While slotted, the user maintains a Pendulum Clock, 5 Spans in size. Each time the user resolves the same specific attack between consecutive Activations, tick the Clock 1 Span. For each each filled Span on the Clock, that attack's Power increased by 20%, up to a max increase of 100%. This boost this Ability resets if the user is switched out, @Affliction[fainted], combat ends, or the user declares a different attack.</p>",
